                    <span>Rough Guides has an odd point of view on South Africa.  Crime is a relavent issue there.  Don't trust this sugar coated point of view.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent informative guide, very reliable</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
